description: This Chainlink VRF common Anurak purrs with a rating of 41, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 41, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 1 for East, Box for South, and 2 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20411-81423-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [41 Votes, Common]
